wiki.content: “WE NEED ALL DA VIBES” serves as the 21st track on the album, featuring melodic verses from Playboi Carti, Ty Dolla $ign and Young Thug. Notably, this marks Young Thug’s second verse since his release from jail in the fall of 2024. However, the beat, chorus and Young Thug’s verse are all originally from an unreleased and leaked Young Thug & Gunna collaboration called “Vibing” that was recorded sometime in 2021. Gunna had two verses which are cut and replaced by Ty Dolla $ign’s and Playboi Carti’s verses. The reason why Gunna is left out could be his ongoing controversy, and with Wheezy being the producer on the song, this could be the main reason, as the two are not on good terms. Although, Gunna isn’t completely excluded as his adlibs are left in. Lyrically, the song embodies a lavish lifestyle filled with luxury and indulgence − an ultimate aspiration for artists like them.
